OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flife for the better'       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Footballer Shaun Whiter was changing   
OL,6, his friend's tyre on the side of the   
OL,7, road in July 2016 when his life changed
OL,8, in an instant.                         
OL,10,FA drink-driver smashed into him,       
OL,11,Fcrushing his legs, which later had to  
OL,12,Fbe amputated.                          
OL,14,FThe 35-year-old, who lives in Hertford,
OL,15,Fhad to give up his career and learn how
OL,16,Fto walk again.                         
OL,18,FHere, in his own words, he explains why
OL,19,Fhe would never go back to his old life 
OL,20,Fand how grateful he is for his new one.
